data.description: Don't miss this 4-level split home with 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths on an oversized cul-de-sac lot. Original hardwood floors in bedrooms and vinyl windows throughout. The upstairs full bath has granite countertop and subway shower tile. The open kitchen features updated cabinets, countertops, and SS appliances, with plenty of storage. Additional family room in lower level and unfinished basement with full bath, ready to be finished or perfect for extra storage. Step outside to enjoy the deck and expansive fenced backyard including a shed for additional storage. New HVAC/AC in 2021. Concrete driveway apron in 2022. Additional upgrades include tankless water heater, water proofing with sump pump and added insulation in attic and walls.
